---
import PageShell from "../components/PageShell.astro";
---

<PageShell
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Important legal disclaimers regarding the use of Al Tareen."
  hidePageHead={false}
>
  <section class="legalPage" aria-label="Disclaimer">
    <div class="legalContainer">
      <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="effective">Effective Date: March 20, 2026</p>

      <p>
        The information provided on <strong>Al Tareen</strong> (https://altareen.com)
        is for general informational and educational purposes only. By using this
        website, you acknowledge and agree to the terms outlined in this Disclaimer.
      </p>

      <h2>1. No Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>
        All content, including frameworks, tools, concepts, and materials, is provided
        for informational purposes only and does <strong>not</strong> constitute
        financial, legal, tax, business, or professional advice.
      </p>
      <p>
        You should not rely on any information on this website as a substitute for
        professional consultation. Always seek advice from a qualified professional
        before making decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Use at Your Own Risk</h2>
      <p>
        Any actions you take based on the information provided on this website are
        strictly at your own risk. You assume full responsibility for any outcomes,
        decisions, or results.
      </p>
      <p>
        Al Tareen is not liable for any losses, damages, or consequences arising
        from the use or misuse of the content.
      </p>

      <h2>3. No Guarantees</h2>
      <p>
        We make no guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, reliability,
        or effectiveness of any content, frameworks, or tools provided.
      </p>
      <p>
        Results may vary significantly depending on individual circumstances,
        execution, and external factors.
      </p>

      <h2>4. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to third-party websites, including external
        tools and financial models. These links are provided for convenience only.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not control, endorse, or assume responsibility for the content,
        accuracy, or practices of any third-party websites.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All original content, including proprietary frameworks and materials,
        is the intellectual property of Al Tareen unless otherwise stated.
      </p>
      <p>
        Unauthorized reproduction, distribution, or misuse is prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Al Tareen disclaims all liability
        for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting
        from your use of the website.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        This Disclaimer may be updated at any time without prior notice.
        Continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of any changes.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions regarding this Disclaimer:
        <a href="mailto:altareenk@outlook.com">altareenk@outlook.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

<style is:global>
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .legalPage {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 0 64px;
    display: flow-root;
  }

  .legalContainer {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 74%, transparent);
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, white 2%),
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 98%, black 2%)
      );
    box-shadow:
      0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.62) inset,
      0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.018);
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .effective {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px 18px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-secondary);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--ink-muted);
  }

  header a,
  .logo {
    border: none !important;
    background: transparent !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
  }

  footer a {
    text-decoration: none !important;
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .legalContainer {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</PageShell>